{"tid":2203222,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"慢必私人檢控 施襲疑犯郭偉强不認罪","createTime":"2020-09-15T07:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T07:53:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4fdfb9e1edc483eaf41d9ce9ae25f769f8fc53a5","tid":2203222,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/6RNNYK4JCRBBPJBNHSEWPSIEJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2F6RNNYK4JCRBBPJBNHSEWPSIEJI%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=c17db95c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2F6RNNYK4JCRBBPJBNHSEWPSIEJI%2F&h=72c80fc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/6RNNYK4JCRBBPJBNHSEWPSIEJI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n慢必私人檢控 施襲疑犯郭偉强不認罪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會內務委員會早前選舉主席鬧爭議，其間人民力量議員「慢必」陳志全遭工聯會郭偉强拖行。陳志全事後提出私人檢控，控告郭偉强普通襲擊。一直知悉案件及收齊文件的律政司，上周五突然要求再次押後案件，以考慮是否介入訴訟。案件昨日再訊，陳一方認為律政司此舉屬不合理拖延，裁判官亦指律政司缺乏有力論據，拒絕押後，並按程序要求郭答辯。郭不認罪，案件押後至11月9日作審前覆核。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/l9u0am5mEfa59Fn0Em7h_Egm3x4=/2030x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UB43GC5VCVGRHH72CKYFYIIRWU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fl9u0am5mEfa59Fn0Em7h_Egm3x4%3D%2F2030x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUB43GC5VCVGRHH72CKYFYIIRWU.jpg&h=0a57627a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告郭偉强（左）昨否認襲擊陳志全，由多名穿白衣人士陪同離開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官：律政司申押後欠論據<br />\n<br />\n陳志全庭外表示感謝法庭維持原有安排，又指律政司遲遲未決定是否介入，「扭扭擰擰」，質疑居心何在。陳自言已作最壞打算和心理準備，律政司可隨時介入並撤銷檢控，甚至有可能「原告變被告」。他直指郭在眾目睽睽下犯案，但警方和律政司卻不跟進兼拖延檢控，影響法治。<br />\n<br />\n被告郭偉强昨於庭上答辯前，律政司代表向法庭表示仍未決定是否介入案件，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官羅德泉考慮後，認為律政司只是片面提出需要更多時間，未能詳細。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n郭否認今年5月8日在中環立法會綜合大樓一號會議室犯案。控方將傳召陳。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESS12249/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qnub4ghSya5iBKuPkhc5S1YYLn8=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I7BUHYVXAZHO7O4FJVEHWZ4RTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fqnub4ghSya5iBKuPkhc5S1YYLn8%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI7BUHYVXAZHO7O4FJVEHWZ4RTU.jpg&h=3b3df7f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳志全批評律政司多番無理拖延。"},{"pid":"1bfd53e612baecaaedc83d6f9f943b9fdcf93329","tid":2203222,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:53:24.000Z","msg":"Pineapple 強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}